{"tid":1435093,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「共識」如果邊個連登仔/網媒再為垃圾警察記者會瘋狂洗版/宣傳就係鬼","createTime":"2019-08-09T03:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:43:33.000Z","uid":9586,"like":102,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e259563a586016f2a98fa7c7265cd7b3c127a8da","tid":1435093,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:00:35.000Z","msg":"因為2014嘅失敗，4點鐘許Sir小丑記者會<br />\n分散視線好成功<br />\n所以就知對運動係好強勁嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">糖衣毒藥</span><br />\n我知大家心很累，想放鬆下<br />\n但呢次係一場戰爭，唔係普通運動<br />\n輸咗你哋無得再笑<br />\n贏咗慢慢清算仲開心<br />\n<br />\n他日我們相約在煲地自由盡興<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢兩日已經笑完，笑夠了<br />\n<br />\n希望大家自己人有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共識</span><br />\n不再討論呢個無營養嘅記者會<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記者朋友如果可以直情唔好去，冷清嘅記者會一定好好睇</span><br />\n<br />\n如果要討論，麻煩開集中討論post<br />\n咩EERR嘅片，希望唔好再岀<br />\n好易令大家放鬆同期待聽日又點ERR/err幾多次<br />\n完全錯哂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位連登仔同網媒，不要重覆犯錯</span><br />\n不忘初心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果達成共識<br />\n就可以宣布<br />\n邊個再瘋狂洗版，分散視線嘅都係鬼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fff11eda479e64839c611fa32bcc5078b04da24","tid":1435093,"uid":9586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"大家幫推，呢個關鍵時間<br />\n2014年嘅一樣都係行錯呢步棋"},{"pid":"486095953c6b8fb18f4ff546bb8bbbc4ac0101e6","tid":1435093,"uid":9586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:02:06.000Z","msg":"之後輸得好慘"},{"pid":"9825fdec6d22c9319b3db5fa7c8a2572fe5aee19","tid":1435093,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:02:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6358e0c88417ebc1bad954492ad47753eb02c71c","tid":1435093,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"呢個係關鍵嘅共識"},{"pid":"c372886be78b9ea865f681967f11986c2d77375b","tid":1435093,"uid":190579,"like":0,"di